<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha"><unclear>sva</unclear>stiśrī</hi> matiraikoṇṭa kopparakecaripaṉmakku yāṇṭu <num value="14"><g type="numeral">10</g> 4</num> Āva
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tu vaṭakarai pāmpūr nāṭṭu tevatāṉan tirukkuṭa mūkkilppālak karukā
<lb n="3"/>vūr <hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi>varkku caṉtirātittavaṟ Oru nontā viḷakkiṉukku nan
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tipuratta viyāpāri cāmuṇṭaṉ mū<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>tti karukāvūr nilam nāṉ vilai
<lb n="5"/>koṇṭa nilamiyūraṭṭap palāṟṟiṉ vaṭavāy Orumā mukkāṇiyum
<lb n="6"/>Ālattūr vāykkāliṉ kīḻai mukkāṇiyumāka nilam
<lb n="7"/><unclear>Arai</unclear>kkālum Itaṉṟaṉṉi<unclear>ṟai</unclear> nīkki niṉṟapokaṅ koṇ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṭu cantirātittaval nontāviḷakkiṉukkuc cāmuṇṭa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṉ mūrtti vaiccitu Iravum pakalumerivatu I<hi rend="grantha">ddharmma</hi>
<lb n="10"/><hi rend="grantha">rakṣi</hi>ppāriv vūrāyiran tiruvaṭiyumivarkaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> pāta tū
<lb n="11" break="no"/><unclear>ḷi</unclear> Eṉṟalaimeliṉa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><note n="27-1">Unidentified symbol.</note>
</p>

